    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="720dc-102">对 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> 对象中的文本的所有访问都是通过 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextRun%2A>，它旨在允许文本布局客户端以任何所选的方式来虚拟化文本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-102">All access to the text in the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> object is through the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextRun%2A>, which is designed to allow the text layout client to virtualize text in any way it chooses.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="720dc-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> 是提供用于设置文本格式和断开文本线条的服务的 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] 文本引擎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] text engine that provides services for formatting text and breaking text lines.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="720dc-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> 可以处理不同的文本字符格式和段落样式，并提供对国际文本布局的支持。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> can handle different text character formats and paragraph styles, and includes support for international text layout.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="720dc-105">与传统的文本 API 不同，<xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> 通过一组回调方法与文本布局客户端进行交互。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-105">Unlike a traditional text API, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextFormatter> interacts with a text layout client through a set of callback methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="720dc-106">它要求客户端在 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> 类的实现中提供这些方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-106">It requires the client to provide these methods in an implementation of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="720dc-107">以下列表描述了必须重写的三个成员：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-107">The following list describes the three members you must override:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="720dc-108"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextRun%2A>：检索从指定的 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> 位置开始 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextRun>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-108"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextRun%2A>: Retrieves a <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextRun> starting at a specified <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> position.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="720dc-109"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetPrecedingText%2A>：检索紧邻指定 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> 位置之前的文本跨距。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-109"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetPrecedingText%2A>: Retrieves the text span immediately before the specified <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> position.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="720dc-110"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextEffectCharacterIndexFromTextSourceCharacterIndex%2A>：检索一个值，该值将 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> 字符索引映射到 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextEffect> 字符索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="720dc-110"><xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource.GetTextEffectCharacterIndexFromTextSourceCharacterIndex%2A>: Retrieves a value that maps a <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextFormatting.TextSource> character index to a <xref:System.Windows.Media.TextEffect> character index.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
